- Devops best practices for CI/CD

## Technical Patterns

### Pipeline Caching
Implementing caching within the CI/CD pipeline to store intermediate build artifacts and dependencies, reducing redundant computations and speeding up subsequent builds.

**Implementation Notes:**
Use tools like Docker layer caching or dependency management systems (e.g., npm, pip) to cache and reuse artifacts. Ensure that cached items are invalidated appropriately when underlying code changes.

